{"type":"message","id":"cfeee0b5","parentId":"7d6fab9d","timestamp":"2026-03-12T23:22:15.218Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The stock data parsing failed. The issue is in `parse_stock_data()` - the regex `\\{[^{}]*\"NVDA\"[^{}]*\\}` can't match nested JSON. The stock JSON in the log file has nested objects with braces, so `[^{}]*` won't cross them.\n\nLet me fix the sender script. The stock data is logged as a raw JSON line in the log file, so the regex approach is fragile. A better approach is to parse the JSON directly.\n\nActually, looking at the log more carefully, the stock JSON is on a line by itself between the \"Fetching stock data\" line and the \"Stock data fetched successfully\" line. \n\nNow I'll update the regex pattern to properly capture the full JSON object including its nested structure.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"The stock data parsing broke — the regex can't handle nested JSON braces. And GitHub repos aren't being parsed at all. Let me fix the sender:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"7c647d12-c04d-4727-98c0-a4a3a5fd13bc","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-sender.py","old_string":"def parse_stock_data(log_content):\n    \"\"\"Extract stock data from log\"\"\"\n    # Look for JSON block in log\n    json_match = re.search(r'\\{[^{}]*\"NVDA\"[^{}]*\\}', log_content, re.DOTALL)\n    if json_match:\n        try:\n            return json.loads(json_match.group())\n        except:\n            pass\n    return None","new_string":"def parse_stock_data(log_content):\n    \"\"\"Extract stock data from log\"\"\"\n    # Look for a line that starts with { and contains \"NVDA\" — it's the raw JSON output\n    for line in log_content.splitlines():\n        line = line.strip()\n        if line.startswith('{') and '\"NVDA\"' in line:\n            try:\n                return json.loads(line)\n            except json.JSONDecodeError:\n                pass\n    return None"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":254,"output":580,"cacheRead":33344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34178,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773357709198}}
