{"type":"message","id":"93f8f9a0","parentId":"c8acf9f9","timestamp":"2026-03-12T23:26:04.149Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me compare the formats and adjust my output to match the previous successful format, then send to Telegram.\n\nDifferences I notice:\n1. Previous uses 📅 header with full date\n2. Previous uses \"💰 Bitcoin\" not \"**Crypto**\"\n3. Previous shows \"Price:\" and \"24h:\" labels\n4. Previous uses \"📊 Tech Stocks\" \n5. Previous shows stock format as \"SYMBOL: $PRICE (CHANGE%) 📈/📉\"\n6. Previous uses \"🚀 Trending GitHub Repos (Created Since 2024)\"\n7. Previous shows repos as \"name ⭐ count\" without description\n\n\n8. Previous has a footer with timestamp and data sources\n\nI should also flag the NVDA and AMD values in the previous output—they look like corrupted numbers, probably OCR errors from screenshots. Now I'll update my script to match this exact format and send it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Good catch, the formats are different. Let me align with your proven format and send it."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"61c77e1e-a10d-43e4-be53-47b77da68683","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/project/openclaw/daily-ping-sender.py","old_string":"def format_message(bitcoin, stocks, repos):\n    \"\"\"Format the daily ping message\"\"\"\n    date_str = datetime.now().strftime(\"%A, %B %d, %Y\")\n    \n    # Bitcoin section\n    btc_arrow = \"📈\" if bitcoin['change'] >= 0 else \"📉\"\n    \n    message = f\"📈 **Daily Ping — {date_str}**\\n\\n\"\n    message += \"**Crypto**\\n\"\n    message += f\"• Bitcoin: ${bitcoin['price']:,} ({btc_arrow} {bitcoin['change']:+.2f}%)\\n\"\n    \n    # Stock section\n    message += \"\\n💹 **Tech Stocks**\\n\"\n    if stocks:\n        for symbol, data in stocks.items():\n            if 'error' not in data:\n                arrow = \"📈\" if data['change_pct'] >= 0 else \"📉\"\n                message += f\"• {symbol} ${data['price']:.2f} ({arrow} {data['change_pct']:+.2f}%)\\n\"\n    \n    # GitHub section\n    message += \"\\n⭐ **Top 10 GitHub Trending Repos**\\n\"\n    if repos:\n        for i, repo in enumerate(repos[:10], 1):\n            stars = format_stars(repo['stars'])\n            desc = repo['description']\n            if desc:\n                message += f\"{i}. {repo['name']} — {desc} ({stars} ⭐)\\n\"\n            else:\n                message += f\"{i}. {repo['name']} ({stars} ⭐)\\n\"\n    \n    return message","new_string":"def format_message(bitcoin, stocks, repos):\n    \"\"\"Format the daily ping message — matches proven Feb 2026 format\"\"\"\n    date_str = datetime.now().strftime(\"%A, %B %d, %Y\")\n    time_str = datetime.now().strftime(\"%H:%M\")\n    \n    # Header\n    message = f\"📅 Daily Ping — {date_str}\\n\\n\"\n    \n    # Bitcoin section\n    btc_arrow = \"📈\" if bitcoin['change'] >= 0 else \"📉\"\n    message += \"💰 Bitcoin\\n\"\n    message += f\"• Price: ${bitcoin['price']:,} USD\\n\"\n    message += f\"• 24h: {bitcoin['change']:+.2f}% {btc_arrow}\\n\"\n    \n    # Stock section\n    message += \"\\n📊 Tech Stocks\\n\"\n    if stocks:\n        for symbol, data in stocks.items():\n            if 'error' not in data:\n                arrow = \"📈\" if data['change_pct'] >= 0 else \"📉\"\n                message += f\"• {symbol}: ${data['price']:.2f} ({data['change_pct']:+.2f}%) {arrow}\\n\"\n    \n    # GitHub section\n    year_ago = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=365)).strftime('%Y')\n    message += f\"\\n🚀 Trending GitHub Repos (Created Since {year_ago})\\n\\n\"\n    if repos:\n        for i, repo in enumerate(repos[:10], 1):\n            stars = format_stars(repo['stars'])\n            message += f\"{i}. {repo['name']} ⭐ {stars}\\n\"\n    \n    # Footer\n    message += f\"\\n—\\n⏰ {time_str} SGT | Data: CoinGecko, Yahoo Finance, GitHub API\"\n    \n    return message"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":37589,"output":1189,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39290,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773357944030}}
