{"type":"message","id":"afe9972d","parentId":"26bd434e","timestamp":"2026-03-13T07:23:12.363Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent just a closing code fence. This probably means the audit text is complete - the ``` closes the markdown code block that started earlier. So the full content they wanted me to review is what I've already assembled.\n\nLet me respond confirming I have the full content and ask if they want me to integrate it into MEMORY.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Got it — that closes the code block. So the full audit is just GAP 4 (the other gaps weren't included or don't exist).\n\nWant me to integrate the **Safe Skills Repository Usage Protocol** into MEMORY.md? I'd add it as a subsection under the Safe OpenClaw Skills Repository section, making it clear that even pre-vetted skills need runtime validation before use."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":742,"output":234,"cacheRead":80768,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81744,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773386576447}}
