{"type":"message","id":"029da35a","parentId":"1fcc13d2","timestamp":"2026-03-13T11:38:33.308Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Everything looks good now. Let me summarize the status for Matt.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Here's the status:\n\n| Item | Status | Notes |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| Gateway | ✅ Running | Port 18789, loopback |\n| Daily Ping (system cron) | ✅ Reinstalled | Was missing, just put it back — `0 7 * * *` |\n| Daily Ping (OpenClaw cron) | ✅ Disabled | Old job correctly disabled |\n| Scripts | ✅ Present | All 3 scripts executable |\n| MEMORY.md | ✅ Current | Last updated 15:25 today |\n| Daily memory files | ✅ Logging | Mar 3-13 present |\n| TrustSkill | ✅ Updated | Self-defense protocol in place |\n\n**One note:** The system crontab was empty when I checked — it had been set up earlier today but somehow got cleared. Reinstalled it. If it disappears again, something's wiping it (possibly a config reload or session boundary). Worth keeping an eye on.\n\n**Doctor warnings** (non-critical): WhatsApp and Telegram group policies are \"allowlist\" with empty allowlists — group messages get silently dropped. By design since you're using these in DM mode, but flagging it.\n\nEverything else is in order. 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"openrouter/hunter-alpha","usage":{"input":626,"output":290,"cacheRead":95552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96468,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773401898076}}
